div1.p: Territory of Washington County of Spokane.}ss
In the District Court of the Territory of Washington and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof, hold- ing terms at Cheney, in said Territory.
To the sheriff of Spokane County, Greeting:

In the Name of the United States, You are hereby commanded to summon + Wm. Straub, John Caraft E. Wilson A.A. Babb + John McGowan D.R. French. D. Boys John Crovert to be and appear before the District Court aforesaid at the Court House, in Cheney, in said County, on the instantes day of April A.D. 1885 at o'clock M., to there give evi- dence in the above entitled cause on the part of said Plaintiff

WITNESS the Hon. George Turner, Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of Washington Territory, and Judge of said Court, and the Seal thereof affixed, this 29 day of Apr A.D. 1885 Kate W. Feauerbach Clerk. By R. Strobach Deputy.
Territory of Washington, County of Spokane }ss.
I hereby certify that I served the within Subpoena on the within named witnesses by reading the same to them in said County, on this 30 day of April A.D. 1885
E.F. Whittier Sheriff By H.B. Mason Deputy
In the District Court of the Territory of Washington and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof, hold- ing terms at Cheney, in said Territory.
Returned and filed this 1st day of May A.D. 1885 Kate W. Feuerbach Clerk. By R. Strobach Deputy.
SHERIFF'S FEES. Serving 8 names at 40 3.20 Mileage 16 miles at 10 1.60 Total, ----$4.80
